                                horas del día.
                            </p> -->
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="col-span-4 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 group rounded-xl p-5 text-dark
                    hover:text-white hover:bg-red-500 content-center hover:shadow-lg transition ease-in-out delay-150hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-110 duration-300"
                    >
                        <div class="my-10">
                            <img
                                src="/public/Img/Icons/NOMIWEB-GRAY.png"
                                alt=""
                                class="m-auto group-hover:filter group-hover:brightness-0 group-hover:invert"
                                width="200"
                            />
                            <h1
                                class="montserrat-bold my-6 text-xl text-center"
                            >
                                Nomina
                            </h1>

                            <!-- <p
                                class="text-sm montserrat-regular mt-3 text-center"
                            >
                                Te ayudamos a generar tu nomina 4.0 de una
                                manera sencilla y rápida.
                            </p> -->
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="col-span-4 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 group rounded-xl p-5 text-dark
                   hover:text-white hover:bg-red-500 content-center hover:shadow-lg transition ease-in-out delay-150hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-110 duration-300"
                    >
                        <div class="my-10">
                            <img
                                src="/public/Img/Icons/RAV-GRAY.png"
                                alt=""
